dataset_id: West Africa Coastal Vulnerability Mapping: Subset of OpenStreetMap (OSM) Roads
title: West Africa Coastal Vulnerability Mapping: Subset of OpenStreetMap (OSM) Roads
summary: The West Africa Coastal Vulnerability Mapping: Subset of OpenStreetMap (OSM) Roads data set includes roads within 200 kilometers of the coast and was extracted from the full OSM data set in March 2014. OSM is a global crowdsourced road and street map and is continually being updated.
